flowchart LR
    subgraph AlwaysResident["Always Resident (~2.6K tokens)"]
        Router[SKILL.md router<br/>~1.8K]
        Contracts[contracts/*.schema.md<br/>~800]
    end

    subgraph LazyPhases["Lazy-Loaded Phase Files"]
        direction TB
        P0[phase-0-context.md]
        P1[phase-1-discovery.md]
        P2[phase-2-exploration.md]
        P3[phase-3-requirements.md]
        P4[phase-4-architecture.md]
        P4c[phase-4c-verification.md]
        P4d[phase-4d-skeletons.md]
        P5[phase-5-implementation.md]
        P55[phase-5.5-reflection.md]
        P6[phase-6-quality.md]
    end

    subgraph LazyRefs["Lazy-Loaded References"]
        FailTax[failure-taxonomy.md]
        Diagrams[diagrams/*.mmd]
        Scripts[scripts/*.py]
    end

    AlwaysResident -->|1. Read when entering phase| LazyPhases
    LazyPhases -->|2. Populate contract| Contracts
    LazyPhases -->|3. Drop after completion| Dropped[[Phase file context released<br/>Contract carries ~1/10 size]]
    Dropped -->|4. Next phase| LazyPhases

    AlwaysResident -.->|On-demand| LazyRefs

    classDef resident fill:#d5f5e3,stroke:#229954,stroke-width:2px
    classDef lazy fill:#fdebd0,stroke:#ca6f1e
    classDef dropped fill:#fadbd8,stroke:#922b21,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    class Router,Contracts resident
    class P0,P1,P2,P3,P4,P4c,P4d,P5,P55,P6,FailTax,Diagrams,Scripts lazy
